{"tid":2231213,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【上岸2】明愛開辦物理治療學榮譽理學士","createTime":"2020-10-05T13:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T15:35:48.000Z","uid":225931,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"01ef0306d7fc8fd11292ec5313f6e15aa9930809","tid":2231213,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T13:22:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vZ6d0fXuj44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvZ6d0fXuj44&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=246f5000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vZ6d0fXuj44</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人口老化問題持續，醫療人手普遍出現短缺，本港現有註冊物理治療師只有2,956名，以700萬香港人口計算，平均每1名物理治療師就要服務2,368名香港市民。根據《醫護人力規劃和專業發展策略檢討報告》指出，推算物理治療師在未來3年將有710人短缺，而到2030年更有933人短缺。修讀物理治療學畢業生，可入職二級物理治療師，起薪點14級，即港幣每月27,485元，頂薪點更可高達港幣每月44,415元，相對其他學系畢業生，收入已非常可觀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJUPAS SSSDP: <a href=\"https://www.jupas.edu.hk/en/programme/sssdp/JSSA03/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jupas.edu.hk%2Fen%2Fprogramme%2Fsssdp%2FJSSA03%2F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=7e0029ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jupas.edu.hk/en/programme/sssdp/JSSA03/</a>"},{"pid":"63c13e24e374517e6d2e0a1ea0dc50b409da7354","tid":2231213,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:10:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bMP8GVDwVY8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbMP8GVDwVY8&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=456cce70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bMP8GVDwVY8</a>"},{"pid":"efacd0b994a8724029d02115daf3c9dcb6088f7d","tid":2231213,"uid":45708,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"01ef0306d7fc8fd11292ec5313f6e15aa9930809","tid"